track_notes: piste bien large au départ puis prendre a droite un sentier non balisé mais très agréable.

This summit is not realy fine, when i went there it was forest workers and the path is getting hard to found. First check that the access road is open (closed if fire risk and summertime). There are 2 or 3 path to reach this summit, and i got lost in the last part in between trees and stone. Therefore be attentive on the way up. No much room on summit (dipole is ok, prefer a vertical setup).
